author: Kiley W.
description: Reaction images such as hugs, kisses, and more, based on user commands.
install_msg: Thank you for installing the reactimages bot. Please type load your imagelist i.e. !imagelist C:\Users\homeserver\Desktop\imagelist.txt
short: Sends reaction images and GIFs based on user commands.
end_user_data_statement: This bot does not store any personal data. It only uses and manages image URLs for reaction commands that you provide yourself.
